parameters: Welcome to my shop, I don't have much though.
\n<Ahai>Someone is letting me borrow this boat.
You can take it to the Tower.
\n<Ahai>Do you want to take it right now?
\n<Leo>Alright, I'm going to go now. You're staying though.
\n<Ahai>Aw... I knew you were going to say that...
\n<Leo>I told you, only if you're patient.
\n<Ahai>Yeah, yeah. Get moving mister treasure hunter.
\n<Leo>Give me a moment, I have something to do.
\n<Ahai>Well hurry up, they might need the boat later.
